jrtr.swrenderer

Class SWRenderContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • jrtr.swrenderer.SWRenderContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RenderContext

    public class SWRenderContext
extends java.lang.Object
implements RenderContext
    A skeleton for a software renderer. It works in combination with SWRenderPanel, which displays the output image. In project 3 you will implement your own rasterizer in this class.

    To use the software renderer, you will simply replace GLRenderPanel with SWRenderPanel in the user application.
